daysWithAqi: Number of days on which AQI was recorded
goodDays: Proportion of days with good AQI
moderateDays: Proportion of days with moderate AQI
unhealthyForSensitiveGroupsDays: Proportion of days with AQI that is unhealthy for sensitive groups
unhealthyDays: Proportion of days with unhealthy AQI
veryUnhealthyDays: Proportion of days with very unhealthy AQI
hazardousDays: Proportion of days with hazardous AQI
maxAqi: Max AQI in the last year
medianAqi: Median AQI in the last year
